@startuml
title Zotero Skills / Synthesis Domain Dependencies
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam package {
  BorderColor #94a3b8
  BackgroundColor #f8fafc
}

package "平台执行域" as Platform #eff6ff {
  [Workflow / Skill Provider] as Workflow
  [ACP Runtime] as ACP
  [Host Bridge / CLI] as Bridge
}

package "源事实域" as Source #f0fdf4 {
  [Zotero Library] as Zotero
  [Derived Artifact Notes] as Notes
}

package "Synthesis Layer" as Synthesis #fffbeb {
  [Foundation / Repository] as Foundation
  [Host Library / Artifact Facade] as SourceFacade
  [Paper Registry Cache] as Registry
  [Reference Resolution] as Resolver
  [Citation Graph] as Graph
  [Tag Vocabulary] as Tags
  [Topics / Topic Graph] as Topics
  [Concept KB] as Concepts
  [Maintenance / Jobs / Debug] as Jobs
  [Sync / Import / Export] as Sync
}

Bridge --> Workflow : submit / inspect
ACP --> Workflow : provider runtime
Workflow --> Notes : artifact writes
Workflow --> Topics : topic synthesis

Zotero --> Notes : stores notes
Zotero --> Registry : item metadata
Notes --> Registry : digest / references / matching metadata
Zotero --> SourceFacade : item metadata
Notes --> SourceFacade : digest / references / citation analysis
Bridge --> SourceFacade : topic workflow reads

Foundation ..> Registry : storage ownership
Foundation ..> SourceFacade : service facade
Foundation ..> Resolver
Foundation ..> Graph
Foundation ..> Tags
Foundation ..> Topics
Foundation ..> Concepts

Registry --> Resolver : reference instances
Resolver --> Graph : matched / unresolved edges
SourceFacade --> Topics : primary workflow inputs
Tags --> Topics : controlled vocabulary
Topics --> Concepts : proposal ingestion
Concepts ..> Topics : optional overlay context
Graph ..> Topics : optional metrics / diagnostics

Jobs --> Registry : incremental registry cache
Jobs --> Graph : structure / metrics / layout
Jobs ..> Topics : explicit source check only
Bridge ..> Jobs : debug capabilities only

Sync ..> Tags : canonical export/import
Sync ..> Topics
Sync ..> Concepts

note bottom of SourceFacade
Topic create/update 的主输入来自
Host Library / Artifact Facade：
library index、resolver result、
filtered digest/references/citation-analysis。
它不是 registry cache rebuild 的完成状态。
end note

note bottom of Registry
Paper Registry Cache 是 registry/citation graph 的运行态缓存：
它规整外部 item/note/artifact facts，
但不是全局 Synthesis SSOT，也不驱动 topic artifact lifecycle。
end note

note bottom of Graph
Citation Graph 消费 Registry Cache / Resolver facts。
默认 UI 只展示库内互引与共享外部引用；
单入度外部引用是 hover-only 展示层。
end note
@enduml
